Release Check List (Nicolas Boichat)

- in po/:
  - make update-po
  - poedit fr.po

- cvs commit
- update NEWS
- update version in configure.ac
- update version in doc/main.xml
- make clean
- make

- make distdir
- in ddccontrol-0.x/:
  - ./configure
  - make
  - make install
  - test at least /usr/local/bin/gddccontrol
  - cd ..

- in doc/: make publish publish-release
- ./commit.sh "Prepare release 0.xx"
- cvs tag Release-0_xx

- make dist
- ftp upload.sourceforge.net:
  - cd incoming
  - bin
  - put ddccontrol-0.x.tar.gz
- add file to SF

- update website :
  - Update website.xml news
  - Update layout.xml
  - Add old doc to archives
  - ./commit.sh

- update FreshMeat infos

- update Gentoo ebuild
